HEADWORD: Decillionth
<hw>De*cil"lionth</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to a
decillion, or to the quotient of unity divided by a decillion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Decillionth</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Decillionth
<hw>De*cil"lionth</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>The
quotient of unity divided by a decillion.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>One of
a decillion equal parts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

